<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Gaming Hub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../src/output.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
    
    <%- include('../navbar')%>

    <header class="bg-purple-700 text-white p-5 text-center text-3xl font-bold">
        About Us
    </header>
    
    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-6 p-4">
        <section class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-purple-500 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">Who We Are</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">We are a passionate gaming community dedicated to bringing the latest gaming news, products, and esports updates to players worldwide.</p>
        </section>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
            <article class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-purple-500">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-400">Our Mission</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">To create a thriving gaming ecosystem where players can connect, compete, and stay updated with the latest trends in the gaming industry.</p>
            </article>
            
            <article class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-purple-500">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-400">Why Choose Us?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">We provide exclusive gaming content, premium gaming products, and a community-driven platform for all gamers.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
        
        <section class="mt-6 bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-purple-500 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">Join Our Community</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">Become a part of our growing gaming family. Engage with fellow gamers, participate in events, and stay ahead in the gaming world.</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-green-400 mt-3 inline-block">Get Involved &rarr;</a>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer class="text-center text-gray-400 text-sm p-5 mt-10 bg-gray-800">
        &copy; 2025 Gaming Hub. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
